Phonons on a uniform q-grid
 &inputph
  prefix='AlAs',           ! Specify a prefix
  tr2_ph = 1.0d-14,
  amass(1) = 26.98           ! Specify atomic mass of Al
  amass(2) = 74.92           ! Specify atomic mass of As
  ldisp = .true.,
  nq1 = 4                ! Specify a uniform q-grid
  nq2 = 4 
  nq3 = 4 
  outdir='./out'
  fildyn='AlAs.dyn',
 /
